    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是畅销游戏《工业小镇》的续作！此次融合了城市营造与工厂模拟，让您在一座巨大火山脚下，为一个热带村镇打造庞大的自动化超级工厂，以满足其日益增长的需求。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/9c5d2bdfc11602f588f6bb6f515bb9c7.poster.avif?t=1770389358\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/9c5d2bdfc11602f588f6bb6f515bb9c7.webm?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/9c5d2bdfc11602f588f6bb6f515bb9c7.mp4?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从荒岛开始，您可以从零建设城镇：比如放置房屋、农场、生产设施和商店。不久后，村民们会加入你的岛屿，并承担各种必要的工作。随着经济发展壮大，您需要巧妙地解决瓶颈问题，并通过道路、桥梁、火车、传送带等自动运输系统优化供应链。只要让村民们吃饱喝足、安居乐业，小小村庄终将发展成跨越多座岛屿的大都市！<br>一位强大而友善的火山神明会注视着一切的进展。只需不断向火山投喂物品，你便能赢得它的欢心，它也将以新配方、新科技和新升级作为回报。火山神甚至能从海底召唤出新岛屿，为你的扩张提供更广阔的空间！</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/71ffba84fc0a4fde1df0bf2fbca61f46.poster.avif?t=1770389358\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/71ffba84fc0a4fde1df0bf2fbca61f46.webm?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/71ffba84fc0a4fde1df0bf2fbca61f46.mp4?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >昼夜循环、体积水物理、数十种新物品、城镇模拟系统大修、可操控角色，以及全新的运输工具（如弹射器和滑索），将为原作粉丝们带来焕然一新的体验。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/31ce4e985ad789585480e625bd10389a.poster.avif?t=1770389358\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/31ce4e985ad789585480e625bd10389a.webm?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/31ce4e985ad789585480e625bd10389a.mp4?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在山中开挖沟渠并筑坝，以控制山泉的水流，使其顺利流向农田和水库，确保它们得到充分的灌溉。利用水车和风车带动传动轴，从而提高食物和矿物的加工能力，或者产生电力，通过电线传输，为冰箱或熔炉供电。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/41cb1612b72e116cdc6588637234befe.poster.avif?t=1770389358\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/41cb1612b72e116cdc6588637234befe.webm?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312130/extras/41cb1612b72e116cdc6588637234befe.mp4?t=1770389358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生产数十种物品，包括热带饮品、糕点、冰淇淋、熟食、咖啡、衣物、珠宝、书籍、药品和魔法药水。每种物品都有特定的属性加成，需根据你所掌握的资源与城镇需求选择最佳的生产项目。<br>一如既往，您可以放松心情，尽情建造，无需担心失败或受到严厉惩罚，因为这里没有时间压力，也不会因尝试而受到惩罚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即将《工业小镇2》加入愿望单，第一时间获取上线通知！</p>",
